  for  leave  to  introduce  a  Bill  to 

provide  for  the  resolution  of  certain  categories  of  financial  service  providers  in 

distress;  the  deposit  insurance  to  consumers  of  certain  categories  of  financial 

services;  designation  of  systemically 

important  financial 

institutions;  and 

establishment of a Resolution Corporation for protection of consumer of specified 

service providers and of public funds for ensuring the stability and resilience of the 

financial system and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto. 

 

